Description: Provides a flexible and easy-to use interface for the soil vegetation 
    atmosphere transport (SVAT) model LWF-BROOK90 written in Fortran. A set of 
    high-level functions provides for convenient simulation set-up and model execution, 
    and parallelization of multi-run simulations.
